                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13771768" author="lyubent" created="Thu, 19 Sep 2013 10:17:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changed the function of the SNAPSHOT_REPAIR_OPT parameter to represent a parallel repair.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13777116" author="dbrosius" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 03:31:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch itself is fine, but the existing setting name isn&apos;t very good imo.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the setting is snapshot... true/false? &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;to me that would mean create snapshots or not.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;not parallel, serial.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;given that we are changing the sense of the parameter, i think it would make sense to change the name so that folks aren&apos;t confused by the flip. (and to make it more clear)&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="13777705" author="lyubent" created="Wed, 25 Sep 2013 16:28:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Changed the param from snapshot to &lt;b&gt;parallel&lt;/b&gt; The command is one of the below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;./nodetool repair -parallel
./nodetool repair -par
./nodetool repair
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13778294" author="dbrosius" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 00:39:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;probably should rename &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;boolean snapshot, to boolean sequential&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;also please fix up NodeToolHelp.yaml&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13779003" author="lyubent" created="Thu, 26 Sep 2013 17:36:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Renamed variable to &lt;b&gt;sequential&lt;/b&gt; and updated NodeToolHelp.yaml&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13780621" author="dbrosius" created="Sat, 28 Sep 2013 00:47:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 thanks, committed to cassandra-2.0 as commit 3a7093356ca032d9ce8767b2c47980aebe4bce60&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
